definition.value: There is a well-known disease called Grey Collie Syndrome that is associated with a particular coat-colour mutation in Collie dogs. See https://omia.org/OMIA000248/9615/ .

Heideterriers are a nascent breed, currently not recognized by the Fédération Cynologique Internationale, with genetic contributions from several hunting breeds such as the German Hunting Terrier and Airedale Terrier. Source: PMID:28508416. Another resource is https://en.heideterrier.eu/our-dogs/.
